## How to run Streamlit app(Habit Tracker)
cd "/Applications/Python/test file/Python practise exercises/Habit Tracker/Week 1"
streamlit run Habit_Tracker_App.py

##To make any changes to your Github repository paste this into the terminal:
cd "/Applications/Python/test file/Python practise exercises/Habit Tracker"
git add .
git commit -m "describe what you changed"
git push